    "multicolumn_CKG66G": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_Nc7Ewp": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"My posture seems to be steadily improving.  Noticing less of a feeling of things pulling downwards around my whole skull.\" - Evelyn</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_ztwwTc": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"I noticed the other day the area where my neck meets my upper back is more flat .  I always had a bit of kyphosis and rounded soldiers and it seems to be correcting.\" - Harvwin</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_kyhMXY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"Im a long time practitioner of various forms of yoga and have been using Reviv for one week now.  I liked it so much I added using Reviv to my yoga practice.\" - Margarita</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_AV63hP": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"I have been using Reviv every night for about a month now.  My main issue was brain fog and pain/migraines caused by a bike accident.  Since wearing it, i have had a migraine or any of the localised pain.  How amazing is that?  Also my neurological function has improved.\" - Heather C</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_kbie4N": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"I am obsessed with wearing it.  My disposition relaxes, my thoughts focus and I enjoy being ME.  And i have been so surprised at how much my energy is present all day, in shockingly steady form.  Wow.  I'm still trying to wrap my head around all this.\" - Heather P</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_4GgtVe": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"At work ive been uncharacteristically positive to the point where i can see in customers and cowokrers faces that im making their day better.  And at home im just more positive and talkative.\" - Dallas</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_KT6jUH": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"I am having so much less pain, for the first time since 2021.  I could cry!\" - Genevieve</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_MykEqy": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>\"The biggest improvement has been my energy and mood during the day has greatly imporved.  Its made it much easier to 'dad'.\" - Andrew G</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        }
      },
